  "title": "Document Controller @ Jurong Island",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><p>• Reporting to Document Manager</p><p>• Responsible for matters related to project documentation</p><p>• Establish a ledger for the document (Drawing/Letter/RFI/MSRA/ITP, etc.) management</p><p>• Responsible for the completion and handover of documents</p><p>• Other requirement from O/E and SEPCOIII.</p><p>• Data entry, storage labeling administration, and logistics of documents.</p><p>• Other ad hoc duties as assigned</p><p>• General administrative duties.</p><p>• Provide administrative support to the team.</p><p>Requirements :</p><p>• 3–5 years of relevant working experience in project documentation; experience with Singapore-based projects is an advantage.</p><p>• Familiar with office-related software.</p><p>• Proficient in English; proficiency in Mandarin is an advantage to liaise with stakeholders.</p><p>• Ability to commence work at short notice is an advantage</p>",
